OL,7,FAnother former colleague formally
OL,8,Fcomplained in 2014 to Oxford
OL,9,FUniversity Hospitals NHS Foundation
OL,10,FTrust that she was being sexually
OL,11,Fharassed by the consultant but said it
OL,12,Fwas "swiftly swept under the carpet"
OL,13,Fby bosses.
OL,15,FIn May 2021 the trust "excluded" Mr
OL,16,FGilbert from working after concerns
OL,17,Fwere raised about inappropriate
OL,18,Fcomments and conduct towards staff but
OL,19,Fhe was allowed to return to work six
OL,20,Fweeks later with restrictions on his
OL,21,Fpractice.
