OL,7,FA Medical Practitioners Tribunal
OL,8,FService (MPTS) panel was told that an
OL,9,Femail was then sent to 46 current and
OL,10,Fformer surgical trainees in the
OL,11,Fdepartment which invited them to
OL,12,Fcontact a Freedom to Speak Up Guardian
OL,13,Fif they wished to flag up any concerns.
OL,15,FAn investigation by the trust followed
OL,16,Fand Mr Gilbert was dismissed in May
OL,17,F2022 as the matter was referred to the
OL,18,FGeneral Medical Council (GMC).
