OL,7,FLast month the GMC outlined a
OL,8,Fcatalogue of inappropriate behaviour
OL,9,Fby Mr Gilbert, on various dates
OL,10,Fbetween 2009 and 2022, which he denied.
OL,12,FThis week the MPTS panel ruled that Mr
OL,13,FGilbert had sexually harassed four
OL,14,Fwomen and inappropriately touched
OL,15,Fthree of them.
OL,17,FHe was also found to have made
OL,18,Finappropriate sexual comments and
OL,19,Fracist remarks, as well as abusing his
OL,20,Fmore senior position in the department.
