OL,7,F"He may benefit from further time to
OL,8,Fdigest and reflect on the findings
OL,9,Fagainst him."
OL,11,F"In all the circumstances, the
OL,12,FTribunal determined that a period of
OL,13,Feight months was sufficient and
OL,14,Fappropriate to mark the serious
OL,15,Fmisconduct found."
OL,17,FMr Gilbert, who qualified in 2000 at
